items.title: Reply to https://barryfrost.com/2023/09/i-m-getting-the-dreaded-rattling
items.content_text: I thought it was just me. I took in my brothers airpods pro and after diagnostics the right and left ones needed replacement. They quoted replacements for ~$160 but somehow the system allowed it to be marked as $90. Except it wouldnt let me check out... He ended up getting a new set of the latest pros for cheaper. This all feels like a scam so you are forced to purchase apple care.
